                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Cincinnati</placeName>\n                <date>March 7th 1866</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\"><add>?</add>\n                <date>2<hi rend=\"sup\">nd</hi></date> Inst enclosing<lb/> one from <persName>Mr.\n                    Jonas</persName> of <placeName>Wilmington, N.C.</placeName> I have<lb/> written\n                to him the result of my <sic>enquiries</sic> which are<lb/> as follows <persName>Dr\n                    Lilienthal</persName> married the parties<lb/> about 18 or 19 years since.\n                    <persName>Major Noah</persName> drew up a<lb/> paper in the Dr<add>?</add> room\n                giving to the lady Ten Thousand<lb/> dollars without any reservation or condition,\n                which<lb/> paper was signed by <persName>Uriah P Levy</persName> and witnessed<lb/>\n                by <persName>Major Noah</persName> &amp; <persName>Dr. Lilienthal</persName> nothing\n                of the kind<lb/> being mentioned <del>by the</del> in the marriage certificate.\n                The<lb/> Dr. has no copy or record of the certificate he is willing<lb/> to testify\n                to any of these facts</p>\n            <p><persName>Mrs Dan Wolf</persName> claims that her books have not been<lb/> sent to\n                her please if you can find out for me <sic>wether</sic><lb/> you sent a copy of the\n                    <sic>sett</sic> if you have not send<lb/> me a <sic>sett</sic> by first\n                opportunity and I will deliver them<lb/> to her. I have had a considerable<lb/>\n                sickness in my family of late and regret to say that<lb/> I have got it again my\n                little boy being now very<lb/> sick with kind regards to all friends amongst<lb/>\n                which remind me to number yourself believe me</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Truly yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">A Harris</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3hq3sf7r/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
