                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3hq3sf7r/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>Have just re-opened the letter to answer<lb/> yours P. <persName>Mr\n                        Wartchki<add>?</add></persName>. I received the package<lb/> of books and\n                distributed them according to your<lb/> instruction for which I remitted you the\n                money<lb/> of which you acknowledged the receipt at the time<lb/> but those two\n                copies were not in there I<lb/> did not get the money from <persName>Mr.\n                    Mayer</persName>—nor<lb/>\n                <persName>I. Abraham</persName>.   <persName role=\"author\">A H</persName></p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
